code: @Override public void customize(EhcacheComponent component) {     if (configurations != null && configuration.getMode() == CacheConfigurationCustomizerConfiguration.Mode.APPEND) {         component.addCachesConfigurations(configurations).     }     if (configurations != null && configuration.getMode() == CacheConfigurationCustomizerConfiguration.Mode.REPLACE) {         component.setCachesConfigurations(configurations).     } }
